<plot>Sam, 24, is shy and introverted. The only woman in his life is his Nan. Until now. Lilya, 24, is Nan's nurse. She is kind and caring, and Nan would like to bring her and Sam together. But how? Nan soon discovers that playing Cupid is strictly for the angels. As if by chance, when Nan says her goodbye, Sam and Lilya say their hellos. But there is a sense of dejavu. Where and how could they have possibly met before? In fact their fi rst meeting took place 25 years before. On a Wednesday. What was always meant to be is now becoming.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?649511</url></doc>
